                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 5315/932.</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Ambassador <persName type="from">Bacon</persName> to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Paris</hi></placeName> [<hi rend="italic">received</hi>
                                <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-05-24"><hi rend="italic">May
                                        24, 1910</hi></date>].</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Mr. Bacon reports that the Hukuang loan agreement was signed to-day by
